track.name: Me or Sum (feat. Future & Lil Baby)

wiki.summary: On “Me or Sum”, up and coming Jacksonville rapper Nardo Wick recruits Atlanta natives, Lil Baby and Future to pose as the second single leading up to Nardo’s debut album, Who is Nardo Wick?. On the track, Nardo Wick, Lil Baby, and Future all show their love for jewelry, expensive items such as Birkin bags, and women. These topics are common ground in most rap music. The trio collaborates on a melodic Trap beat produced by muli-platinum producer, Z3N. Read more on Last.fm.
